Title: Authorizes the city of Batavia to alienate certain parklands for use as a municipal parking lot and to preserve the historic Brisbane mansion
Summary: Authorizes the city of Batavia to alienate certain parklands of Austin park for use as a municipal parking lot and to preserve the historic Brisbane mansion.
ActClause: AN ACT authorizing the city of Batavia to alienate certain parklands for use as a municipal parking lot and to preserve the historic Brisbane mansion
